title: Who would win, Sabine Wren vs Fenn Rau? - Quora

response.answer_text: It’s a good question: Sabine was well trained by her family and the ghost crew. She is creative and can easily hold her own, but Fen Rau is the more experienced fighter and physically stronger. I would love to say that Sabine wins, but I believe that it would strongly depend on the situation of their fight.
Sabine had some training with Ezra and Kanan with lightsaber. And as a bounty hunter she can have some tricks with some gadgets like the ones she owns. I believe Sabine wins
